<span class="displaytext">the (candidate full) presidential committee today announced the launch of a new television ad, entitled "one hour." the ad is airing in new hampshire and boston. <p>visit <a href="http://www.joinrudy2008.com">http://www.joinrudy2008.com</a> to view the ad. the script is below. </p><p><strong><u>script for "one hour":</u></strong> </p><p><strong>mayor (candidate last):</strong> "i remember back to the 1970s and the early 1980s. iranian mullahs took american hostages and they held the american hostages for 444 days. and they released the american hostages in one hour, and that should tell us a lot about these islamic terrorists that we're facing. the one hour in which they released them was the one hour in which ronald reagan was taking the oath of office as president of the united states. the best way you deal with dictators, the best way you deal with tyrants and terrorists, you stand up to them. you don't back down. i'm (candidate full) and i approve this message."</p></span>



